           MOVE  "S8200"                    TO   BSGEROR-PARA
      *
           INITIALIZE                            DB-TABLE
      *
           EVALUATE  TRUE
               WHEN  COND-DBIO-PK
                     PERFORM  S8210-FETCH-KEY0-RTN
